http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/Alappuzha-revenue-district-youth-festival-begins-today/article13981431.ece

The Alappuzha Revenue District youth festival will begin at Kayamakulam on Tuesday.About 6,000 students belonging to 11 sub-districts will take part in contests in the five-day festival.Inaugural ceremonyA cultural procession will begin from Government Boys HSS at 2.30 p.m. on Tuesday to mark the commencement of the festival.It will reach Girls Higher Secondary School, the main venue of the festival, where the inaugural ceremony will be held at 5 p.m. The valedictory session will be held on January 9 at 4 p.m.